# Cloudflare Pages routing for Cognis.
#
# Prerendered snapshots live at:
#   - <section>/index.html (about-us, our-services, contact, blog)
#   - our-services/<slug>/index.html (3 service detail pages)
#   - blog/<slug>/index.html (6 blog posts)
#   - teams/<id>/index.html (team member detail pages)
#
# Cloudflare Pages serves directory index files automatically, so no
# rewrites are needed. The prior `/about-us -> /about-us.html` mapping
# triggered a redirect loop because CF Pages' clean-URLs feature redirects
# /about-us.html -> /about-us, fighting the rewrite.
#
# Unknown paths fall through to /404.html with HTTP 404 (CF Pages default
# when a top-level 404.html exists).
#
# Retired service slugs — April 2026. The portfolio was pruned to the 3
# surfaced services; any external backlink or cached Google index to these
# URLs 301s to the services landing.
